### Base URL Configuration
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### ========================================
### Basic Health Check
### ========================================

### Test server is running
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Accept: text/plain

### Original profile page
GET {{baseUrl}}/profile
Accept: text/plain

###
# 4. สร้าง testuser1 ด้วย POST /encode (เข้ารหัส)
POST {{baseUrl}}/encode
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser1",
  "mobile": "0812345678",
  "cardId": "1234567890123",
  "password": "password123"
}

